                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-1.5 text-xs">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock text-blue-400 w-3"></i> Sabah: 10:00 – 12:00</div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock text-blue-400 w-3"></i> Akşam: 16:00 – 19:00</div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-go">Detay <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[8px]"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="guide-card gc-purple">
                <div class="p-5 flex flex-col gap-4 flex-1">
                    <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                        <div class="icon-w iw-purple"><i class="fa-solid fa-person-walking-with-cane"></i></div>
                        <div class="btn-go text-[9px] px-2 py-1 ml-auto"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-[8px]"></i></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-slate-800 leading-snug mb-1.5">Refakatçi Politikası</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">Hastalarımıza eşlik eden refakatçilerin uyması gereken esaslar ve yararlanabileceği imkânlar.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-1.5 text-xs">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple-400 w-3"></i> Ücretsiz yatak imkânı</div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple-400 w-3"></i> Yemek desteği mevcut</div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-go">Detay <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[8px]"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="guide-card gc-red">
                <div class="p-5 flex flex-col gap-4 flex-1">
                    <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
                        <div class="icon-w iw-red"><i class="fa-solid fa-mask-ventilator"></i></div>
                        <span class="text-[9px] font-black bg-red-50 text-red-600 border border-red-100 px-2 py-1 rounded-lg">Kritik</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-slate-800 leading-snug mb-1.5">Yoğun Bakım Ziyareti</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">YBÜ'lere özel sterilizasyon kuralları ve ziyaret protokolleri hakkında zorunlu bilgiler.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-1.5 text-xs">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-red-400 w-3"></i> Önceden izin alınmalıdır</div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-red-400 w-3"></i> Koruyucu kıyafet zorunlu</div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-go">Kritik Bilgiler <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[8px]"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="basvuru">
        <div class="section-bar">
            <span class="badge badge-green"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-dot"></i> İşlemler</span>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-800">Başvuru & Randevu</h2>
            <div class="section-bar-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

            <div class="guide-card gc-teal" id="randevu">
